title: Finland will seek to join NATO, ditching decades of neutrality despite Russia's threats of retaliation - CNN
content:
1. Finland will seek to join NATO, ditching decades of neutrality despite Russia's threats of retaliation  CNN
  2. Russia warns that it would be a 'mistake' for Finland and Sweden to join Nato - BBC News  BBC News
  3. Finland's president tells Putin his country will apply to join NATO  Fox News
  4. Finland, Sweden move closer to seeking NATO membership  The Associated Press
  5. Sweden's ruling party poised to back NATO bid  Reuters
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: Finland's government said Sunday it intends to join NATO, ditching decades of neutrality and ignoring Russian threats of possible retaliation as the Nordic country attempts to strengthen its security following the onset of the war in Ukraine. Sweden's ruling party later said it will also support joining the alliance.
